OL,3,CInvestigations continue into deaths of
OL,4,Cthree women pulled from sea off
OL,5,CBrighton
OL,7,FPolice are continuing to investigate
OL,8,Fthe deaths of three women found in the
OL,9,Fsea off Brighton.
OL,11,FThe bodies were found in the early
OL,12,Fhours on Wednesday morning near Black
OL,13,FRocks car park, in Madeira Drive.
OL,15,FIt's understood the women were
OL,16,Fapproximately 20 to 30 years old and
OL,17,Fwere first spotted at Brighton's
OL,18,FPalace Pier before drifting to the
OL,19,Fmarina.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
