CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778760670
OL,3,CInvestigations continue into deaths of
OL,4,Cthree women pulled from sea off
OL,5,CBrighton
OL,7,FThe beach has since been reopened to
OL,8,Fthe public and officers have left the
OL,9,Fscene.
OL,11,FSussex Police Chief Superintendent
OL,12,FAdam Hays has said the force's
OL,13,Fpriority is now to identify the women
OL,14,Fand contact their next of kin.
OL,16,FHe said: "I understand the impact this
OL,17,Ftragic incident has had on the local
OL,18,Fcommunity and more widely.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
