OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778760670
OL,3,CInvestigations continue into deaths of
OL,4,Cthree women pulled from sea off
OL,5,CBrighton
OL,7,F"This is a sensitive investigation and
OL,8,Fwe know the public are keen to
OL,9,Funderstand the full circumstances.
OL,11,F"But our priority at this time is
OL,12,Fidentifying these three women and
OL,13,Flocating their families, who at this
OL,14,Fpoint remain unaware they have lost
OL,15,Floved ones.
OL,17,F"I would ask for people's patience
OL,18,Fwhile we conduct these enquiries and
OL,19,Fto avoid speculation while this is
OL,20,Fongoing.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
