PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778760670
OL,3,CInvestigations continue into deaths of
OL,4,Cthree women pulled from sea off
OL,5,CBrighton
OL,7,F"Anyone with information that could
OL,8,Fhelp is asked to contact police online
OL,9,For via 101, quoting Operation Ledmore."
OL,11,FLocal councillors and politicians have
OL,12,Fpaid tribute to the victims, including
OL,13,FCouncillor Bella Sankey, Leader of
OL,14,FBrighton and Hove City Council.
OL,16,FShe said she was shocked and deeply
OL,17,Fsaddened to hear of the developments.
OL,19,FSpeaking to ITV Meridian she said:
OL,20,F"This is an absolutely tragic and
OL,21,Fhorrific incident.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
