PN,41605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778760670
OL,3,CInvestigations continue into deaths of
OL,4,Cthree women pulled from sea off
OL,5,CBrighton
OL,7,F"I know that the people of Brighton
OL,8,Fand Hove will be thinking of these
OL,9,Fwomen today and my heart goes out to
OL,10,Fthem and their loved ones.
OL,12,F"I know that it's a very fast-moving
OL,13,Fsituation, but I want to pay tribute
OL,14,Fto our emergency services colleagues
OL,15,Fwho have been leading on this, and I
OL,16,Fknow that the police are working
OL,17,Fquickly to try and establish the
OL,18,Fidentities of these women, and to find
OL,19,Fout exactly what has happened."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
