OL,3,CInvestigations continue into deaths of
OL,4,Cthree women pulled from sea off
OL,5,CBrighton
OL,7,FThe Labour MP for Brighton Kemptown
OL,8,Fand Peacehaven, Chris Ward said: "My
OL,9,Fthoughts and condolences are with
OL,10,Feveryone affected and the families and
OL,11,Floved ones.
OL,13,F"It's obviously a terrible incident
OL,14,Fand it will have a real impact on the
OL,15,Flocal community.
OL,17,F"It's right at the heart of my
OL,18,Fconstituency.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
