OL,3,CInvestigations continue into deaths of
OL,4,Cthree women pulled from sea off
OL,5,CBrighton
OL,7,F"I just want to thank the emergency
OL,8,Fservices, the Coastguard and RNLI, and
OL,9,Feveryone who was at the scene today.
OL,11,F"It's a really difficult moment for
OL,12,Fthe city and for the community and my
OL,13,Fthoughts are with all of those
OL,14,Faffected."
OL,16,FSian Berry, the Green MP for Brighton
OL,17,FPavilion, said: "Unbearably sad news
OL,18,Fthis morning.
OL,20,F"My thoughts are with the families and
OL,21,Ffriends of these three women.
